<h2 id="2-conversi√≥n-de-tipos">2. Conversi√≥n de tipos</h2>
<div class="bs-callout bs-callout-primary">Todos los datos adquiridos por el metodo input son guardados como strings.</div>

<h3 id="pasar-string-a-int">Pasar string a int</h3>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">edad</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"Escriba su edad: "</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">edad</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">edad</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="pasar-string-a-float">Pasar string a float</h3>
<div class="bs-callout bs-callout-primary">Los n√∫mero flotantes deben ser escritos con punto no con coma</div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">peso</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"Escriba su peso: "</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">peso</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">float</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">peso</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="3-variables-como-argumento-de-la-funci√≥n-input">3. Variables como argumento de la funci√≥n input</h2>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">nombre</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"Escriba su nombre: "</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">apellido</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">f</span><span class="s">"Escriba su apellido, </span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">nombre</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s">: "</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">f</span><span class="s">"Buenos d√≠as, </span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">nombre</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s"> </span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">apellido</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s">."</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
